title: De'Longhi PrimaDonna Elite - Product Video
description:
A perfect combination of dynamic design, state-of-the-art coffee technology and easiness of use, PrimaDonna Elite is the new generation of De’Longhi bean to cup coffee machines to satisfy every desire with style and taste.
